Class SendableLogger

com.techhounds.houndutil.houndlog.loggers.SendableLogger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Loggable
public class SendableLogger extends Logger
Basically a SingleItemLogger but it uses sendables. Useful for putting anything Sendable like a Field2d, PIDController, or a motor controller.
